const DATA = [
  { year: 2017, label: `Seeding Beginnings`, narrative: `TVC began as a seed idea among ten founders who shared one goal: living sustainably, together. Partnering with WeCommunities — their first project — the group chose a barren plot near Thakkatti village in Tamil Nadu. Fencing stopped the overgrazing that had stripped the soil, and members began trucking in organic matter to seed a small area they named the Kaveri plot. A permaculture course at Navadarshanam shaped their thinking, but the year ended hard: an unusually fierce monsoon washed away the season's first earthwork and much of what had been planted.`, events: [
